venues.name: Fairmont Singapore
venues.description: Prestigious 5-star hotel in the heart of the city with one of Singapore's largest pillar-free ballrooms. Perfect for grand, luxurious celebrations.
venues.reviews_summary: Known for excellent service and stunning ballrooms. Food quality is exceptional. Convenient location near MRT. Premium pricing but worth it for special occasions.

venues.name: Amara Singapore
venues.description: Well-established hotel in Tanjong Pagar with excellent accessibility. Known for reliable service and quality food. Popular choice for mid-range budgets.
venues.reviews_summary: Consistently praised for convenient MRT location and attentive service. Food quality is good with generous portions. Good value for money in Central area.

venues.name: Genting Hotel Jurong
venues.description: Affordable hotel in the west with modern facilities. Great option for couples with many guests from the western region. Excellent value for money.
venues.reviews_summary: Popular for budget-conscious couples. Good food quality and spacious ballroom. Free parking is a big plus. Staff are helpful and accommodating.

venues.name: Crowne Plaza Changi Airport
venues.description: Unique airport hotel location with excellent accessibility for international guests. Modern facilities and reliable service. Great for guests flying in from overseas.
venues.reviews_summary: Perfect for guests traveling from abroad. Direct MRT access is very convenient. Professional service and good food. Some find the location far from city center.

venues.name: Marina Bay Sands
venues.description: Iconic luxury hotel with the largest pillar-free ballroom in Singapore. The Sands Grand Ballroom accommodates up to 6,600 guests. Features 21 versatile ballrooms, rooftop garden with city skyline views, and SkyPark cocktail reception options. Perfect for grand, lavish celebrations.
venues.reviews_summary: Known for spectacular venues and world-class service. The Sands Grand Ballroom is unmatched in size. Excellent for large weddings with international guests. Premium location and iconic status make it a dream venue.

venues.name: Raffles Hotel Singapore
venues.description: Legendary heritage hotel with timeless elegance and colonial charm. The Jubilee Ballroom hosts 250+ guests with cream and gold interiors and stunning chandeliers. Palm Ballroom perfect for 200 guests. The Lawn offers outdoor solemnisation for up to 50 guests. Singapore's most prestigious wedding venue.
venues.reviews_summary: The pinnacle of luxury and heritage. Impeccable service befitting the Raffles name. Stunning ballrooms with historic charm. Premium pricing but unmatched prestige and elegance. Perfect for couples seeking a sophisticated, iconic venue.

venues.name: Mandarin Oriental Singapore

packages.name: Oriental Ballroom Package
features: Wedding showcase savings up to SGD 8,888

venues.description: Luxury Marina Bay hotel with the stunning fan-shaped Oriental Ballroom featuring a 20-metre curved LED wall. Accommodates up to 390 guests for sit-down dinner. Garden Suite offers city skyline views surrounded by greenery. Harbour View Suites provide natural light with full-length windows. Exceptionally Singapore with dedicated wedding experts.
venues.reviews_summary: Exceptional service and stunning venues. The Oriental Ballroom's LED wall is breathtaking. Food quality is outstanding. Wedding coordinators are meticulous and professional. Perfect Marina Bay location with three nearby MRT stations. Worth the premium pricing.

venues.name: Shangri-La Singapore

packages.name: Island Ballroom Package
features: Pillarless ballroom for up to 1,000 guests

venues.description: Prestigious Orchard Road hotel set in 15 acres of lush gardens. The pillarless Island Ballroom accommodates up to 1,000 guests. Tower Ballroom perfect for 250-500 guests. Features heritage Dutch Pavilion for intimate ceremonies and the beautiful Banyan Deck for outdoor solemnisations. 20 function rooms and dedicated wedding specialists.
venues.reviews_summary: Renowned for impeccable service and stunning venues. The Island Ballroom is one of Singapore's largest. Beautiful garden settings for outdoor ceremonies. Food quality exceptional. Professional event management team. Premium Orchard location with ample parking.

venues.name: Four Seasons Hotel Singapore
venues.description: Luxury Orchard hotel featuring the pillarless Four Seasons Ballroom with arched windows overlooking tree-lined Orchard Boulevard. Breathtaking Barrisol ceiling with customizable LED lighting. Crescent Ballroom offers handmade glass chandeliers for intimate celebrations. Wedding Maestros provide expert planning assistance. Perfect for sophisticated Orchard area weddings.
venues.reviews_summary: Exceptional Four Seasons service and attention to detail. The ballroom's Barrisol ceiling and LED lighting create stunning ambience. Food quality is outstanding. Wedding Maestros are highly professional and helpful. Convenient Orchard location. Premium but worth every dollar for quality-conscious couples.
